S-Skinner.

104
00:05:44,761 --> 00:05:45,845
(laughing)

105
00:05:45,928 --> 00:05:48,848
Well, that's it.
I've lost them forever.

106
00:05:48,931 --> 00:05:51,392
Now, I'd like to introduce you
to lunch lady Doris

107
00:05:51,476 --> 00:05:53,603
who will serve you
healthy, nutritious meals.

108
00:05:53,686 --> 00:05:55,396
Yeah. Right.

109
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,647
SKINNER: Miss Phipps,
the school nurse

110
00:05:56,731 --> 00:05:58,816
who will provide
ointments and unguents

111
