the school bully

112
00:06:00,777 --> 00:06:02,779
who will administer noogies
and nipple twisters.

113
00:06:02,862 --> 00:06:05,448
I look forward
to whaling on all of you.

114
00:06:05,531 --> 00:06:06,532
(gulps)

115
00:06:06,616 --> 00:06:08,743
<i>♪ There was a farmer</i>
<i>who had a dog ♪</i>

116
00:06:08,826 --> 00:06:10,453
<i>♪ And bingo was his name-o ♪</i>

117
00:06:10,536 --> 00:06:15,333
<i>♪ B-i... O, b-i... O, b-i... </i>♪

118
00:06:15,416 --> 00:06:17,335
♪ A<i>nd Bingo was his name-o ♪</i>

119
