Added extra clap.
Not college material.

120
00:06:20,797 --> 00:06:23,299
-(humming)
-Hey! Wee bairn!

121
00:06:23,383 --> 00:06:25,134
Hie ye hence from me heath!

122
00:06:28,054 --> 00:06:30,014
Can't you
understand English?

123
