of how I got my saxophone.

135
00:07:16,060 --> 00:07:17,103
D-oh!

136
00:07:21,899 --> 00:07:23,359
Homer, I can't get
the baby to burp.

137
00:07:23,443 --> 00:07:24,777
Could you try for a while?

138
00:07:24,861 --> 00:07:26,028
No problem.

139
00:07:26,112 --> 00:07:27,864
I'll just give her
a sip of beer.

140
00:07:27,947 --> 00:07:29,532
Come on, Maggie.

141
00:07:29,615 --> 00:07:32,368
It's Miller time.
Yes, it's Miller time.

142
00:07:32,452 --> 00:07:33,453
Homer!

143
