-and Bart--
-Mom!

153
00:08:01,022 --> 00:08:03,357
Hey, she's just giving
the public what it wants--

154
00:08:03,441 --> 00:08:05,109
Bart by the barrelful.

155
00:08:05,193 --> 00:08:06,068
I'm sorry, Lisa.

156
00:08:06,152 --> 00:08:07,820
It's just how the story goes.

157
00:08:07,904 --> 00:08:09,322
No matter what Bart tried

158
00:08:09,405 --> 00:08:11,866
