163
00:08:19,832 --> 00:08:21,250
"F," Bart.

164
00:08:21,334 --> 00:08:23,503
And believe me,
you'll be seeing plenty of them.

165
00:08:26,130 --> 00:08:28,174
Bart, would you like
to read a book?

166
00:08:30,259 --> 00:08:31,177
No.

167
00:08:31,260 --> 00:08:32,678
Would you like to color something?

168
00:08:32,762 --> 00:08:33,846
I did.

169
00:08:36,224 --> 00:08:37,141
Mmm.

170
00:08:39,268 --> 00:08:40,811
-(jazz music playing)
-(fingers snapping)

171
