MAN: <i>That's damn fine coffee</i>
<i>you got here in Twin Peaks.</i>

172
00:08:46,817 --> 00:08:48,861
<i>And damn good cherry pie.</i>

173
00:08:56,410 --> 00:08:57,578
Brilliant.

174
00:08:58,621 --> 00:09:01,541
I have absolutely no idea
what's going on.

175
00:09:01,624 --> 00:09:04,877
Homer, I want you to look
at this drawing Bart did.

176
00:09:04,961 --> 00:09:07,380
Oh! It's beautiful.

177
00:09:07,463 --> 00:09:11,509
Oh, let's put Bart's beautiful
drawing up on the fridge...

178
00:09:11,592 --> 00:09:12,635
Homer, stop.

179
00:09:12,718 --> 00:09:14,679
Would you please
look at the drawing?

180
00:09:14,762 --> 00:09:17,348
Oh, all right. What a--
(screams)

181
00:09:17,431 --> 00:09:19,183
Burn it! Send it to hell!

182
00:09:19,267 --> 00:09:21,936
I think we're going to have
to get Bart some help.

183
00:09:22,019 --> 00:09:23,187
Get it away.

184
00:09:23,854 --> 00:09:26,065
Bart, son,
you want to play catch?

185
00:09:26,148 --> 00:09:27,567
-No.
-Oh.

186
00:09:27,650 --> 00:09:30,111
When a boy doesn't want
to play catch with his old man

187
00:09:30,194 --> 00:09:31,821
something is seriously wrong.

188
00:09:31,904 --> 00:09:33,948
I'll play catch
with you, son.

189
00:09:34,031 --> 00:09:36,117
-Get the hell out.
-I'm gone.

190
00:09:37,034 --> 00:09:37,952
Ah...

191
00:09:38,035 --> 00:09:38,911
Mrs. Simpson, physically

192
00:09:38,995 --> 00:09:41,038
