as the dollar.

193
00:09:41,122 --> 00:09:43,291
I'm afraid Bart's severe
emotional dysfunction

194
00:09:43,374 --> 00:09:46,544
stems from a deep-seated
psychological trauma.

195
00:09:46,627 --> 00:09:48,754
(chuckles)

196
00:09:48,838 --> 00:09:50,006
