<i>With nowhere else to turn</i>

197
00:09:50,089 --> 00:09:52,174
<i>we went to see</i>
<i>the school psychologist.</i>

198
00:09:52,258 --> 00:09:53,634
Mr. And Mrs. Simpson

199
00:09:53,718 --> 00:09:55,678
there's nothing
to be alarmed about.

200
00:09:55,761 --> 00:09:59,515
