intimidating to a young child...

201
00:09:59,599 --> 00:10:01,934
particularly one with
as many flamboyantly

202
00:10:02,018 --> 00:10:04,687
homosexual tendencies
as your son.

203
00:10:04,770 --> 00:10:05,855
Bart's gay?

204
00:10:05,938 --> 00:10:06,772
Bart?

205
00:10:07,773 --> 00:10:09,108
Whoops! Wrong file.

206
00:10:10,901 --> 00:10:13,029
Ah... (stammers) The point
I'm trying to make here

207
00:10:13,112 --> 00:10:16,407
is that Bart must learn
to be less of an individual

208
00:10:16,490 --> 00:10:18,701
and more a faceless slug.

209
00:10:21,579 --> 00:10:22,455
Mmm. Mmm.

210
00:10:23,247 --> 00:10:25,916
Hmm. Lisa,
how old are you?

211
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:28,169
I am three
and three-eighths.

212
00:10:28,252 --> 00:10:31,631
Mmm. Lisa, if I have five apples

213
00:10:31,714 --> 00:10:33,674
and I take away three apples

214
00:10:33,758 --> 00:10:36,093
how many apples do I have left?

215
00:10:36,177 --> 00:10:37,345
Two apples.

216
00:10:37,428 --> 00:10:38,262
Wait a minute.

217
00:10:40,222 --> 00:10:41,098
She's right.

218
00:10:41,182 --> 00:10:42,642
Yes, very good.

219
00:10:42,725 --> 00:10:46,729
Marge, Homer, I believe
your Lisa may be gifted.

220
00:10:46,812 --> 00:10:48,230
That's wonderful,

221
00:10:48,314 --> 00:10:50,358
but still can't you do
anything for Bart?

222
00:10:50,441 --> 00:10:52,902
Marge, he's five. His life is over.

223
00:10:52,985 --> 00:10:54,779
Lisa's the wave of the future.

224
00:10:54,862 --> 00:10:56,405
Wave of the future!

225
00:10:56,489 --> 00:10:58,032
That's right, honey.

226
00:10:58,115 --> 00:10:59,575
If you nurture her gift now

227
00:10:59,659 --> 00:11:01,661
there's no telling what she can do.

228
00:11:01,744 --> 00:11:02,578
Wow.

229
00:11:02,662 --> 00:11:05,247
Just think
of the possibilities.

230
00:11:05,956 --> 00:11:09,710
MAN: <i>Lisa Simpson</i>
<i>has won the Nobel prize.</i>

231
00:11:09,794 --> 00:11:10,878
Nah.

232
00:11:11,420 --> 00:11:14,215
<i>Lisa Simpson has won</i>
<i>the Nobel prize...</i>

233
00:11:14,298 --> 00:11:15,299
<i>for kick boxing!</i>

234
00:11:15,383 --> 00:11:16,300
Yah!

235
00:11:16,384 --> 00:11:17,301
<i>Hmm.</i>

236
00:11:19,553 --> 00:11:22,515
Uh... I'll give you the address
of a nice preschool.

237
00:11:23,891 --> 00:11:25,059
(girls chanting)
Cross my heart

238
00:11:25,142 --> 00:11:28,354
and hope to die, here's
the digits that make "pi".

239
00:11:28,437 --> 00:11:31,857
Three point one four one five
nine two six five three five

240
00:11:31,941 --> 00:11:34,485
eight nine seven nine three two
three eight four six two six...

241
00:11:34,568 --> 00:11:35,528
I can assure you

242
00:11:35,611 --> 00:11:37,780
Our preschool is of
the highest quality.

243
00:11:37,863 --> 00:11:41,117
Over 75% of our graduates
go on to first grade.

244
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:43,494
Well, our little girl has a gift
and we're willing to do

245
00:11:43,577 --> 00:11:44,704
